The chapati recipie steps are :

take wheat flour and add water to it
make sure that the two mix well 
when mixed the dough produced  should be turned into  a circle
put the toppings on the top that you need to  stuff into the chapati
turn the perimeter of the circle to  the center so that the area covers the stuffings on the top 
gently  push it so it becomes a cylinder
turn it back to its original circular shape
put the dough  on the pan which should be covered by ghee first
turn on the gas
keep fliping the chapati till it is coloured in its mustard colour and is filled  wit black spots
turn off the gas 
put the chapati on a board 
put somme ghee on the topp of the hot chapati

The chapati is prepared